      <head>Carl Johann Perl</head>
      <div>

        <p>Catholic musicologist, and translator of St. Augustine and other church fathers. Perl
          attended <ref cRef="entity-000003">Guido Adler</ref>'s musicological seminar at Vienna
          University, and was frequent reviewer for <ref cRef="entity-002556"><title level="j">Die
              Musik</title></ref>. His review <bibl><title level="a">Heinrich Schenkers 'Das
              Meisterwerk in der Musik, Ein Jahrbuch, Bd. III',</title>
            <title level="j">Die Musik</title> 23/1 (1930/31), 672f</bibl> (preserved as OC 2/p. 8)
          was a source of controversy in the Schenker circle.</p>

      </div>
